abstract: Stephen Holden reviews performance by jazz singer Jane Monheit at Birdland.
lead_paragraph: The jazz singer presented a tribute to Ella Fitzgerald’s American Songbook albums, offering up-tempo numbers and piercing, primal ballads.

headline.main: Review: Jane Monheit, at Birdland, Alternates Latin Textures With a Moaning Cry
